Package: devops-toolkit
Version: 1.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 4.0), curl, git, docker.io | docker-ce, python3, php-cli
Maintainer: John Sabba <johnsabba@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/sabbajohn/useful-stuff
Description: DevOps Toolkit - Collection of development and deployment scripts
 A comprehensive collection of development scripts including:
 - Django project creator with multiple templates
 - PHP version switcher
 - Network troubleshooting tools
 - Storage management utilities
 - Download manager
 - Laravel starter scripts
 .
 This toolkit helps developers and DevOps engineers automate common tasks
 and streamline their development workflow.